Ohio Man Accused Of Operating Fraud Scheme Indicted, U.S. Says

-- B y   J e r a n   W i t t e n s t e i n
-- 
2011-09-15T22:18:01Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-15/ohio-man-accused-of-operating-fraud-scheme-indicted-u-s-says.html
Monroe Beachy, a 77-year old from
Sugarcreek,  Ohio , was indicted by a federal grand jury today,
the U.S. Justice Department said in an e-mailed statement.
Beachy is accused of operating a $16.8 million investment fraud
scheme.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
